00:42:53,933 --> 00:42:55,355
doesn't matter to me at all.

813
00:42:55,510 --> 00:42:57,000
But what matters most

814
00:42:57,000 --> 00:42:59,130
is Hejing Securities helping
Shanlifang Hotel Group

815
00:42:59,140 --> 00:43:00,280
